Attendant console for Cisco Unified Communication Manager, integrated with Cisco Jabber, supports video calls, instant messaging, presence, Busy Lamp Field (in case of missing presence server), Active Directory and LDAP user and contact import, AD authentication, softphone mode, desk phone control mode, speed dials, look alike option for adapting the application layout to user's needs, keyboard shortcuts, call parking options, multi-call support, seatless option, completely web based and compatible with Chrome, Internet Explorer, Safari and Firefox. Can run on MS Windows and on OSX.
The application server is fully virtualized and available as virtual appliance on VMware Solution Exchange. It's a suite, it includes many other services such as fax server, Billing, recorder, mobile4mobility....